Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
check_base_layer_density(25.10)                check_base_layer_density(25.10)

Name
       check_base_layer_density - Checks the CPODE density by the defined pat-
       tern

Syntax
       check_base_layer_density

       [-help]

       [-layer <layerName>]

       [-site_parameter <sitePara>]

       Checks the CPODE density by the defined pattern.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs  a  brief description that includes type and default in-
              formation for each check_base_layer_density parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command: man check_base_layer_density.

       -layer <layerName>
              Specifies the layer name for the base layer density check.

       -site_parameter <sitePara>
              Specifies the site parameter of the CPODE layer. The site  para-
              meters of the CPODE layer include:

              * shape_num: Number of the CPODE shape

              * site_num: Number of the site in row.

              * step: Number of stepping

              The  tool  checks the CPODE number of consecutive site_num sites
              by every step steps. The CPODE number should be  less  than  the
              defined shape_num. Otherwise, the tool will give a violation.

Example
              *

                In  the following example, the command checks the CPODE in the
                number of consecutive 3 sites by every 1 step. The CPODE  num-
                ber should less than 4.

                check_base_layer_density  -site_parameter   {4  4  1}   -layer
                CPODE

                Number of CPODE:3

                Number of site in row:3

                Number of stepping:1

              * In the following example, the command checks the CPODE  number
                of  consecutive  2  sites  by  every  1 step. The CPODE number
                should less than 4.

                check_base_layer_density  -site_parameter   {5  4  1}   -layer
                CPODE

                Number of CPODE:5

                Number of site in row:4

                Number of stepping:1

